## Limitations

This report is based on available data and publications up to October 2023. The findings are subject to the limitations of the sources used, which may not cover all aspects of immigration or reflect the most recent policy changes. Additionally, the analysis focuses primarily on the economic and demographic benefits, potentially overlooking other social and cultural dimensions of immigration.

